            <div class="opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper ">

    
    <h1 class="opener__hed " >        How a Maine Businessman Made the AR-15 Into America’s Best-Selling Rifle
    </h1>

    <h2 class="opener__dek " >        Neither a gun enthusiast nor a right-wing ideologue, Richard Dyke used political connections and lobster giveaways to build Bushmaster, the company that popularized assault-style rifles.
    </h2>

    </div> <!-- Close .opener__topic-title-dek-wrapper -->

</div>
        
<div class="article-meta-1
